for APTII, \u201cHuman Development Impact Assessment: Resource Book\u201d, dated February 2007, and from \u201cHuman Development Impact Assessment of Trade Policies,\u201d a concept note for programme development on trade and human development issues, prepared by Mumtaz Keklik and Emel Memis for APTII in 2005. The Resource Book also has adapted ideas and elements from existing literature on impact assessment, such as the World Bank\u2019s Poverty and Social Impact Analyses, the European Commission\u2019s Trade Sustainability Impact Assessment, the United Nations Environment Programme (UNEP)\u2019s tools for the Integrated Assessment of Trade-Related Policies (UNEP 2002), Women\u2019s Edge Coalition\u2019s Trade Impact Review (Gammage et al. 2002), and the Organization for Economic Cooperation and Development (OECD)\u2019s Promoting Pro-Poor Growth: Practical Guide to Ex-Ante Poverty Impact Assessment (2007). Many individuals provided extremely useful comments, suggestions, and inputs during the preparation of the toolkit.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "caf727fe-3305-4999-956e-58c2b68ff943": {"__data__": {"id_": "caf727fe-3305-4999-956e-58c2b68ff943", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/human-development-impact-assessment-trade-policy-toolkit", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Human Development Impact Assessment of Trade Policy: A Toolkit", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/human-development-impact-assessment-trade-policy-toolkit", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Dev