a would be useful to analyze whether or not a country\u2019s socio-economic situation has improved after a change in trade policy.18 On the other hand, sectoral analysis may require collecting data similar to the framework introduced here (e.g., whether the percentage of informal workers in the industry increased after trade liberalization policy was implemented). 18 See \u201cOverview\u201d in MFAT in Mongolia and UNDP Mongolia (2009). Continued HUMAN DEVELOPMENT IMPACT ASSESSMENT OF TRADE POLICY: A Toolkit 39 HUMAN DEVELOPMENT IMPACT ASSESSMENT OF TRADE POLICY: A Toolkit 39 Table A1.2: Indicators of human development Indicator Years available Source Core HD indicators HDI 1980\u2013 UNDP, HDRs, http://hdr.undp.org/ GDP per capita (PPP US$) 1980\u2013 World Bank, WDI, go.worldbank.org/B53SONGPA0 Life expectancy at birth by sex 1990, 2000, 2008 WHO Statistical information system (WHOSIS), Life expectancy, apps.who.int/whosis/database/life_tables/ life_tables.cfm Maternal mortality ratio Various UNDP, HDRs, http://hdr.undp.org/ Infant mortality rate Various UNDP, HDRs, http://hdr.undp.org/ Under-five mortality rate Various UNDP, HDRs, http://hdr.undp.org/ Adult literacy rate by sex 1975\u2013 UNESCO Institute of Statistics, Literacy, stats.uis.unesco.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "c4a6cd0d-a27b-400a-8342-309e90fd81fa": {"__data__": {"id_": "c4a6cd0d-a27b-400a-8342-309e90fd81fa", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/human-development-impact-assessment-trade-policy-toolkit", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Human Development Impact Assessment of Trade Policy: A Toolkit", "